"788034AI (C00987) 10-09." "435852ID 10-09." Includes text, comparative area map, location map, and list of major historical events since 1908. Ancillary maps: Key petroleum sector facilities -- Regional physiography -- Southern Caspian energy prospects -- Strait of Hormuz -- Population density -- Ethnoreligious distribution. Map shows province boundaries, roads, expressways, and railroads.
